## Key Constraints

- TODO.md is the source of truth for scope and status.
- Layered architecture: models -> repositories -> services -> controllers -> routes.
- SOLID and DRY principles apply.
- No comments allowed in code.
- TypeScript strict mode.
- Centralized error handling via AppError and errorHandler.
